  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Support to Enhance the Confidence among the Administration, Security Force (FDS) and the Population in the North and Sahel Regions of Burkina Faso</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project responds to the need to strengthen trust between the populations, the Administration and Security Forces (DSF) in the Northern and Sahel regions of Burkina Faso. This will be done through interventions contributing to the improvement in quality of the service delivery and the affiliation between populations and DSF in order to improve security situation and social cohesion.</narrative>
  </description>
